ountry Profiles: Regions and territories: Somaliland] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/africa/country_profiles/3794847.stm |date=20090504150302 }}. Retrieved 2009-09-14.</ref>，作為內陸國家的埃塞俄比亚通過索马里兰的海岸線發展海上貿易關系（參見[[索馬里蘭外交|索馬里蘭外交]]）。

此外，[[英国|英国]]<ref>{{cite web|title=索馬利蘭|url=http://www.publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm200304/cmhansrd/vo040204/halltext/40204h03.htm|publisher=英国国会|accessdate=2007-02-23|archive-date=2021-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210313195235/https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm200304/cmhansrd/vo040204/halltext/40204h03.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Future recognition" >{{cite web|title=索馬利蘭接近获得埃塞俄比亚承认|url=http://www.afrol.com/articles/25633|publisher=afrol News|accessdate=2007-07-06|archive-date=2012-02-12|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/65OUeUIkg?url=http://www.afrol.com/articles/25633|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[比利时|比利时]]<ref name="Future recognition" />、[[加纳|加纳]]<ref name="Future recognition" />、[[南非|南非]]<ref name="Future recognition" />、[[瑞典|瑞典]]<ref name="Future recognition" />、[[吉布提|吉布提]]<ref name="Djibouti" >{{cite web|title=索馬利蘭和吉布提陷入痛苦的港口之争|url=http://www.afrol.com/articles/23556|publisher=afrol News|accessdate=2007-07-22|archive-date=2012-02-12|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/65OZFZcqf?url=http://www.afrol.com/articles/23556|dead-url=no}}</ref>等国也與索馬利蘭有政治上的交往。2007年1月17日，[[欧洲联盟|欧盟]]派出一个外交事务代表团前往索马里兰商讨未来合作事宜。<ref>{{cite web|title=EU金援索馬利蘭的破冰之旅|url=http://www.globalpolicy.org/nations/sovereign/sover/emerg/2003/0211euaid.htm|publisher=全球政策论坛|accessdate=2007-02-23|archive-date=2003-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20031223173022/http://www.globalpolicy.org/nations/sovereign/sover/emerg/2003/0211euaid.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[非洲联盟|非洲联盟]]也曾派出一位外交部长前往索马里兰讨论国际承认的前景。<ref>{{cite web|title=AU supports Somali split|url=http://www.mg.co.za/articlePage.aspx?articleid=263915&area=/insight/insight__africa/|publisher=邮报和卫报在线|accessdate=2007-02-23|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070930201028/http://www.mg.co.za/articlePage.aspx?articleid=263915&area=%2Finsight%2Finsight__africa%2F|archivedate=2007-09-30}}</ref>
